Rating: 4
We haven't eaten this yet, but I already know its amazing. I was in a hurry and baked a gluten free pie crust with toasted coconut, subbed non-dairy creamer for the cream, added a few drops of vanilla to the filling and cooked it on the stove, covered filling with heated seedless raspberry jam and topped with raspberries. Just a taste of the filling and a raspberry was divine.

