I served this for Thanksgiving, and everyone loved it. I'm glad that I listened to the reviewer who cut down on the lime zest. I'm a lime fanatic, but I only added 1 1/2 tsp of zest. I also reduced the amount of sugar in the custard and raspberry sauce. Not that I don't love "sweet", but the sometimes pastry recipes are just so rich, that you can only eat a tiny piece.

